arm-gray uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">Our Services</span><div class="grid gap-1 pl-2 mb-2"><button class="text-left block text-sm py-1.5 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange">• Meta Ads Performance</button><button class="text-left block text-sm py-1.5 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange">• Google Ads (PMax &amp; Search)</button><button class="text-left block text-sm py-1.5 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange">• Organic SEO (Map Pack)</button><button class="text-left block text-sm py-1.5 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange">• Lead Generation Funnels</button><button class="text-left block text-sm py-1.5 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange">• Dental Clinic Marketing</button><button class="text-left block text-sm py-1.5 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange">• Social Media &amp; UGC</button></div></div><button class="text-left text-base font-medium py-2 border-b border-dark-brown/10 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/80 hover:text-burnt-orange">Case Studies</button><button class="text-left text-base font-medium py-2 border-b border-dark-brown/10 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/80 hover:text-burnt-orange">Blog</button><button class="text-left text-base font-medium py-2 border-b border-dark-brown/10 transition-colors cursor-pointer text-dark-brown/80 hover:text-burnt-orange">Contact</button><div class="pt-6"><button class="w-full text-left text-sm text-dark-brown/60 hover:text-burnt-orange py-2 cursor-pointer">Careers - Join Our Team</button><button class="w-full text-left text-sm text-dark-brown/60 hover:text-burnt-orange py-2 cursor-pointer">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</button><button class="mt-6 w-full py-3 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-burnt-orange to-rich-orange text-soft-beige font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-center shadow-lg cursor-pointer">Get Free Marketing Audit</button></div></div></div></nav><main class="flex-grow transition-opacity duration-300"><div id="home-page-container" class="pt-24 space-y-24"><section id="hero" class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center px-4 overflow-hidden bg-[#F3EEE7]"><div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/10 w-96 h-96 bg-burnt-orange/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div><div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-rich-orange/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 space-y-8 px-4"><div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-3 py-1 bg-burnt-orange/10 border border-burnt-orange/20 rounded-full text-[#FF8C2A] text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase animate-fade-in font-sans"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-sparkles w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z"></path><path d="M20 2v4"></path><path d="M22 4h-4"></path><circle cx="4" cy="20" r="2"></circle></svg><span>Bangalore's Elite Performance Firm</span></div><h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-dark-brown tracking-tight leading-none">We Engineer <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-burnt-orange via-[#FF8C2A] to-[#FF8C2A]">High-ROAS</span> Pipelines</h1><p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-dark-brown/80 font-sans font-light max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Navora Media is a premium, results-first performance marketing agency. We bypass empty vanity metrics and deploy rigorous algorithmic media buying, medical dental patient acquisition systems, and authoritative organic SEO hubs that convert searchers into margin.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-4"><button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-xl orange-gradient text-white font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-burnt-orange/25 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 font-sans"><span>Secure Your Trial Audit</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-dark-brown/5 border border-dark-brown/20 text-dark-brown font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs hover:bg-dark-brown/10 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center space-x-1 font-sans"><span>Explore ROAS Studies</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></button></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 pt-12 border-t border-dark-brown/10"><div><p class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-burnt-orange">5.1x</p><p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1 font-sans">Average Account ROAS</p></div><div><p class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-dark-brown">400%</p><p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1 font-sans">YoY Compound Scaling</p></div><div><p class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-burnt-orange">DR 78</p><p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1 font-sans">SEO Target Authority</p></div><div><p class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-dark-brown">182+</p><p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1 font-sans">Dental Implant Bookings</p></div></div></div></section><section id="services-preview" class="bg-white py-20 border-y border-dark-brown/10"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12"><div class="text-center space-y-3"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] font-sans">Engineered Frameworks</p><h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-dark-brown tracking-tight">Our Focused Execution Pillars</h2><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-dark-brown/60 max-w-xl mx-auto font-sans">Choose an elite pillar built upon real conversion math, programmatic structures, and zero guesswork.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="group relative bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-burnt-orange/50 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-dark-brown/5 flex flex-col justify-between"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-burnt-orange"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-burnt-orange transition-colors">Meta Ads Performance Optimization</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 mt-1 line-clamp-1 italic font-sans animate-pulse">Unlock hyper-scale on Facebook and Instagram with algorithmic spend allocation and rigorous creative pipelines.</p></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-light line-clamp-3 font-sans">Multi-funnel scaling strategies to capture high-value customer actions, increase ROAS, and bypass tracking limitations.</p></div><div class="pt-6 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><button class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] group-hover:text-dark-brown uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center space-x-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Analyze Blueprint</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-warm-gray uppercase">ACTIVE PILLAR</span></div></div><div class="group relative bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-burnt-orange/50 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-dark-brown/5 flex flex-col justify-between"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-burnt-orange"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-burnt-orange transition-colors">Google Ads &amp; Intent Capture</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 mt-1 line-clamp-1 italic font-sans animate-pulse">Intercept customers at the exact millisecond of high purchase intent across Search, Shopping, and YouTube.</p></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-light line-clamp-3 font-sans">Dominating high-intent search terms and feeding machine-learning algorithms with clean conversion vectors.</p></div><div class="pt-6 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><button class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] group-hover:text-dark-brown uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center space-x-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Analyze Blueprint</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-warm-gray uppercase">ACTIVE PILLAR</span></div></div><div class="group relative bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-burnt-orange/50 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-dark-brown/5 flex flex-col justify-between"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-burnt-orange"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-burnt-orange transition-colors">Organic SEO &amp; Digital Authority</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 mt-1 line-clamp-1 italic font-sans animate-pulse">Command organic real estate on search engines for high-intent keywords that keep delivering compounding pipeline value.</p></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-light line-clamp-3 font-sans">Comprehensive SEO combining impeccable technical architecture, semantic page structures, and authoritative link networks.</p></div><div class="pt-6 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><button class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] group-hover:text-dark-brown uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center space-x-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Analyze Blueprint</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-warm-gray uppercase">ACTIVE PILLAR</span></div></div><div class="group relative bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-burnt-orange/50 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-dark-brown/5 flex flex-col justify-between"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-burnt-orange"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-burnt-orange transition-colors">Enterprise Lead Generation Fannels</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 mt-1 line-clamp-1 italic font-sans animate-pulse">Turn cold visitors into pre-qualified, sales-ready appointments through psychological funnels and automation.</p></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-light line-clamp-3 font-sans">Custom conversion-rate engineered funnel paths mated with frictionless CRM triggers and lead systems.</p></div><div class="pt-6 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><button class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] group-hover:text-dark-brown uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center space-x-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Analyze Blueprint</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-warm-gray uppercase">ACTIVE PILLAR</span></div></div><div class="group relative bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-burnt-orange/50 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-dark-brown/5 flex flex-col justify-between"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-burnt-orange"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-burnt-orange transition-colors">Premium Dental Clinic Patient Acquisition</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 mt-1 line-clamp-1 italic font-sans animate-pulse">The ultimate local pipeline to fill calendar gaps for Invisalign, Dental Implants, and high-worth cosmetic cases.</p></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-light line-clamp-3 font-sans">Custom Patient Acquisition engines combining geo-targeted hyper-intent ads with rapid appointment booking tech.</p></div><div class="pt-6 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><button class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] group-hover:text-dark-brown uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center space-x-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Analyze Blueprint</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-warm-gray uppercase">ACTIVE PILLAR</span></div></div><div class="group relative bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-burnt-orange/50 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-dark-brown/5 flex flex-col justify-between"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-burnt-orange"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-burnt-orange transition-colors">Social Media Organic Strategy &amp; UGC</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 mt-1 line-clamp-1 italic font-sans animate-pulse">Crafting modern cultural footprints for high-end brands that support performance scaling ad campaigns.</p></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-light line-clamp-3 font-sans">Creative styling, editorial calendar frameworks, and creator collaborations designed to convert followers into brand assets.</p></div><div class="pt-6 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><button class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] group-hover:text-dark-brown uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center space-x-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Analyze Blueprint</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-warm-gray uppercase">ACTIVE PILLAR</span></div></div></div><div class="text-center pt-4"><button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-dark-brown/5 border border-dark-brown/15 text-dark-brown hover:bg-dark-brown/10 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-all cursor-pointer inline-flex items-center space-x-1.5 font-sans"><span>Explore All Integration Specifics</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button></div></div></section><section id="why-choose-us" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div id="differentiators-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div class="space-y-6"><div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-1 px-2.5 py-1 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 text-burnt-orange text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest font-sans"><span>Scientific Deployment VS Agency Clichés</span></div><h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-dark-brown">Why High-Growth Businesses Trust Navora Media With Ad Capitals</h2><p class="text-sm font-light text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed font-sans">Unlike generic media buying operations that outsource work to uncertified interns, your campaigns at Navora are engineered by seasoned tracking analysts and CRO architects.</p><div class="space-y-4 pt-1"><div class="flex items-start space-x-3.5"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-burnt-orange/15 text-burnt-orange flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs mt-1 font-sans">✓</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-sm font-bold text-dark-brown">Consolidated Machine Training models</h4><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/60 font-sans">We structure accounts to trigger immediate algorithmic optimization on Google &amp; Meta ecosystems.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start space-x-3.5"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-burnt-orange/15 text-[#FF8C2A] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs mt-1 font-sans">✓</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-sm font-bold text-dark-brown">Sovereign Attribution Setup</h4><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/60 font-sans">We configure server-to-server CAPI and subdomain DNS setups to track true checkout origins.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start space-x-3.5"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-burnt-orange/15 text-burnt-orange flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs mt-1 font-sans">✓</div><div><h4 class="font-serif text-sm font-bold text-dark-brown">Rigorous Procedural Dental Funnels</h4><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/60 font-sans">Geo-fenced orthdontics captures generating qualified patient bookings for Invisalign and implants.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 relative overflow-hidden space-y-6 shadow-sm"><div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#FF8C2A]/5 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none"></div><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-warm-gray font-bold font-sans">AVERAGE CAMPAIGN LIFT METRICS</p><div class="space-y-4"><div><div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-dark-brown font-serif">Meta ROAS Improvements (avg 45 days)</span><span class="text-burnt-orange font-bold font-mono">+92%</span></div><div class="w-full bg-dark-brown/5 h-2 rounded overflow-hidden"><div class="bg-burnt-orange h-full rounded" style="width: 92%;"></div></div></div><div><div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-dark-brown font-serif">Google Search CPA Reduction</span><span class="text-[#FF8C2A] font-bold font-mono">-38%</span></div><div class="w-full bg-dark-brown/5 h-2 rounded overflow-hidden"><div class="bg-[#FF8C2A] h-full rounded" style="width: 74%;"></div></div></div><div><div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs mb-1"><span class="text-dark-brown font-serif">Local Map Pack organic rank elevation</span><span class="text-burnt-orange font-bold font-mono">10x Volume</span></div><div class="w-full bg-dark-brown/5 h-2 rounded overflow-hidden"><div class="bg-burnt-orange h-full rounded" style="width: 85%;"></div></div></div></div><div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/10 text-center shadow-sm"><span class="text-[10px] text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1 font-sans">AUDITED FIRST PARTY PERFORMANCE INTEGRITY</span><p class="text-xs text-burnt-orange font-bold font-sans">Authenticated with complete Triple Whale &amp; Google Analytics matching</p></div></div></div></section><section id="featured-case-study" class="bg-white py-20 border-y border-dark-brown/10"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12"><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end gap-6"><div><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[#FF8C2A] font-bold font-sans">PERFORMANCE PROOFS</p><h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-dark-brown mt-2">Compound Scale in Action</h2></div><div><button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg orange-gradient text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors cursor-pointer flex items-center space-x-1 font-sans"><span>View All Case Studies</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-sm"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-burnt-orange to-rich-orange h-full"></div><div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6"><span class="inline-flex items-center space-x-1.5 text-xs text-[#FF8C2A] font-bold tracking-widest font-sans"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-trending-up w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 7h6v6"></path><path d="m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17"></path></svg><span>ROAS DOMINANCE ACCELERATOR</span></span><h3 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-dark-brown tracking-tight leading-tight">How We Scaled Aura Living beyond $4.8M in Annual Revenue and Achieved a 5.1x Sustainable ROAS</h3><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 animate-fade-in"><div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/5"><p class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-burnt-orange">5.1x ROAS</p><p class="text-[10px] text-dark-brown/50 uppercase font-mono">Consolidated scale</p></div><div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/5"><p class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-dark-brown">-34% CAC</p><p class="text-[10px] text-dark-brown/50 uppercase font-mono">Reduced acquisition cost</p></div></div><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 line-clamp-2 font-sans font-light">Facing severe dynamic tracking limits and audience overlap prior, Aura Living consolidated its campaign sets and deployed our signature 'Creative Sandbox' hook iterations.</p><button class="text-xs uppercase text-[#FF8C2A] font-bold tracking-widest hover:text-dark-brown transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer font-sans"><span>Read Full Tactical Breakdown</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button></div><div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-dark-brown/10 space-y-4 shadow-sm"><p class="text-xs text-[#FF8C2A] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold font-sans">CLIENT LOG DATA MATCH</p><div class="space-y-2 font-mono text-[11px] text-dark-brown/80"><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-dark-brown/10 pb-1.5"><span>Initial Spend:</span> <span class="text-dark-brown font-semibold">$15K/month</span></div><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-dark-brown/10 pb-1.5"><span>Ad Spend Post Scale:</span> <span class="text-burnt-orange font-bold">$120K/month</span></div><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-dark-brown/10 pb-1.5"><span>Documented Conversions:</span> <span class="text-dark-brown font-semibold">14,800 purchases</span></div><div class="flex justify-between"><span>Validated Revenue:</span> <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">$612K/month top</span></div></div><div class="bg-[#F3EEE7] p-3 rounded text-center"><span class="text-[9px] text-[#FF8C2A] font-bold block">AUDIT SECURITY VERIFIED</span></div></div></div></div></section><section id="process-overview" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12"><div class="text-center space-y-3"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-burnt-orange font-sans">ENGINEERED DEPLOYMENT</p><h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-dark-brown tracking-tight">How Navora Media Partners For Growth</h2><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-dark-brown/60 max-w-lg mx-auto font-sans">A methodical, milestone-driven framework engineered for optimal margin capture.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6"><div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/10 relative space-y-4 hover:border-burnt-orange/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"><span class="font-serif text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#FF8C2A]/20 block">01</span><h3 class="font-serif text-base font-bold text-dark-brown">Technical Discovery &amp; Code Audit</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 font-light leading-relaxed font-sans">We perform a thorough analysis of your historical ad spend, Conversions API tracking setup, and search engine crawler schema files to uncover latent indexing and attribution leaks.</p></div><div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/10 relative space-y-4 hover:border-burnt-orange/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"><span class="font-serif text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#FF8C2A]/20 block">02</span><h3 class="font-serif text-base font-bold text-dark-brown">The Creative Sandbox Buildout</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 font-light leading-relaxed font-sans">Rather than risking budget on assumptions, we establish single-variable testing models to match the precise hooks and creative parameters that click with your target buyers.</p></div><div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/10 relative space-y-4 hover:border-burnt-orange/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"><span class="font-serif text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#FF8C2A]/20 block">03</span><h3 class="font-serif text-base font-bold text-dark-brown">Consolidated Algorithmic Campaign Deploy</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 font-light leading-relaxed font-sans">We clear redundant overlap and feed Meta &amp; Google's machine learning architectures consolidated data streams, accelerating pixel training to achieve high consistency.</p></div><div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-dark-brown/10 relative space-y-4 hover:border-burnt-orange/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"><span class="font-serif text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#FF8C2A]/20 block">04</span><h3 class="font-serif text-base font-bold text-dark-brown">CBO &amp; Budget Scale Amplification</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70 font-light leading-relaxed font-sans">Once a creative-match is identified and account stability matches our strict target margins, we initiate Cost-Cap bidding rules to safely scale budget parameters.</p></div></div></section><section id="testimonials-panel" class="bg-white py-20 border-t border-dark-brown/10"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12"><div class="text-center space-y-3"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] font-sans">VERIFIED VOICE</p><h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-dark-brown">C-Suite Partner Appreciations</h2></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 space-y-4 relative flex flex-col justify-between shadow-sm hover:border-burnt-orange/30 transition-colors"><div class="space-y-3"><div class="flex space-x-1"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg></div><p class="text-sm font-serif italic text-dark-brown/90 leading-relaxed font-light">"By redesigning our Meta funnel and deploying their Creative Sandbox loop, Navora Media took our brand beyond 4x ROAS while doubling our monthly spend budget. Absolute performance masters."</p></div><div class="pt-4 border-t border-dark-brown/10 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center"><div><h5 class="font-serif font-bold text-sm text-dark-brown">Ananya Mehta</h5><p class="text-[10px] text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Founder &amp; CMO</p></div><span class="text-[10px] text-burnt-orange font-bold font-mono">Solstice Apparel</span></div></div><div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#Fbf9f6] border border-dark-brown/10 space-y-4 relative flex flex-col justify-between shadow-sm hover:border-burnt-orange/30 transition-colors"><div class="space-y-3"><div class="flex space-x-1"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-[#FF8C2A] fill-[#FF8C2A]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l