ustify-between items-center"><div><h5 class="font-serif font-bold text-sm text-dark-brown">David Sterling</h5><p class="text-[10px] text-dark-brown/50 uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Director of Marketing</p></div><span class="text-[10px] text-burnt-orange font-bold font-mono">HoloCloud SaaS</span></div></div></div></div></section><section id="audit-landing-cta" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-20"><div class="relative p-8 sm:p-12 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-burnt-orange/20 overflow-hidden text-center space-y-6 shadow-md"><div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-burnt-orange/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div><div class="mx-auto w-12 h-12 rounded bg-burnt-orange/15 border border-burnt-orange/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[#FF8C2A] mb-2 animate-pulse"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clipboard-check w-6 h-6" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="8" height="4" x="8" y="2" rx="1" ry="1"></rect><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path d="m9 14 2 2 4-4"></path></svg></div><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-[#FF8C2A] font-sans">IMMEDIATE AD CAMPAIGN VETTING</p><h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-dark-brown tracking-tight leading-none max-w-2xl mx-auto">Ready to Discover Where Your Ad Dollars are Bleeding?</h2><p class="text-sm text-dark-brown/75 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-sans font-light">Submit your basic parameters. Our Bangalore performance architects review your campaign configurations and deliver a 12-page static diagnostic report. Absolutely zero obligation.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-2"><button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-xl orange-gradient text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-transform hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center space-x-1.5 shadow-lg shadow-burnt-orange/25 font-sans"><span>Get Free Custom Audit Report</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><button class="text-xs font-bold text-dark-brown/70 hover:text-burnt-orange uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer hover:underline font-sans">Learn More about the Audit Core</button></div><p class="text-[10px] text-dark-brown/40 font-sans">* We execute standard diagnostic checks safely under strict NDAs and privacy compliance metrics.</p></div></section></div></main><footer id="main-footer" class="bg-white border-t border-dark-brown/10 pt-16 pb-8 text-dark-brown/80"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-center space-x-3 group cursor-pointer"><svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="38" height="38" class="select-none flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="100" height="100" fill="none"></rect><g><path d="M 50,36 C 58,22 75,18 85,28" stroke="#E57324" stroke-width="3.4" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(0 50 50)"></path><path d="M 50,36 C 58,22 75,18 85,28" stroke="#E57324" stroke-width="3.4" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(11.612903225806452 50 50)"></path><path d="M 50,36 C 58,22 75,18 85,28" stroke="#E57324" stroke-width="3.4" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(23.225806451612904 50 50)"></path><path d="M 50,36 C 58,22 75,18 85,28" stroke="#E57324" stroke-width="3.4" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(34.83870967741935 50 50)"></path>